title: Wind Cave National Park: Wind Cave Room Names
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     History & Culture     Places     Wind Cave Room Names                Wind Cave Room Names      The names of rooms and places in Wind Cave were given by the cave explorers who discovered these places. Often the names are descriptive, refer to people involved with Wind Cave, or tell a story about what was happening when that place was discovered. Click on a letter below for a list of room names and information about each room.  Some of the room name links also have pictures or references other historic information.
